  "text": "Remark 3.3. Note that this choice of bisector (since Sp 2r is simply connected, we may set η = 1; see [CITATION_1] ), determines our 4-fold covering group up to isomorphism and identifies it as the pullback along the standard embedding Sp 2r ֒→ SL 2r of the 4-fold cover of SL 2r (F ) with the BLS block compatible cocycle (see [CITATION_2] ).",
